
  Swablu    Normal Type Pokémon

  SWABLU has light and fluffy 
  wings that are like cottony clouds. 
   Swablu is not frightened 
  of people.  It lands on the heads 
  of people and sits there like 
  a cotton-fluff hat. 
	Evolution Chain
      Swablu ► Altaria

